Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Day 15.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.46,0:00:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The bot made its first clean profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.97,0:00:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Ten dollars thirty-five.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.04,0:00:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I didn't celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.69,0:00:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I knew exactly what this moment was.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.35,0:00:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I can't code.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.80,0:00:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}9 years in crypto.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.94,0:00:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}AI trades my thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.07,0:00:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Day 15.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.49,0:00:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}After fixing yesterday's bug, I restarted the bot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.42,0:00:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Today was its first real trade after the fix.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.83,0:00:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Ten forty-six AM — long at 85.27.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.51,0:00:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Trailing stop closed at 86.45.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.50,0:00:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Clean ten dollars thirty-five.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.00,0:00:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}My 15-minute reconciler ran a round immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.10,0:00:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Two rows in the DB.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.97,0:00:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Two fills on Coinbase.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.33,0:00:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Zero mismatch.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.92,0:00:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Zero residual.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.55,0:00:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The experiment account's still net negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.60,0:00:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}That doesn't matter today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.54,0:00:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}What I'm celebrating isn't the ten-thirty-five.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.62,0:01:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It's that the system I built ran one full trade cycle cleanly — clean open, clean close, clean reconcile.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.46,0:01:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}One clean start is worth more than a pile of lucky breaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}This is Day 15 of this series.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.68,0:01:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It's also the starting line.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.83,0:01:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}From Day 16, I post what happened today, in real time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.22,0:01:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Thanks for watching me be wrong in public for 15 days straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.10,0:01:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Follow for the next chapter.
